The paper discusses Simultaneous Localization and Mapping (SLAM) which is a topic related to robotics and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses Lidar SLAM and visual SLAM which are related to computer vision, so cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely. The paper also discusses deep learning and calibration which are related to machine learning and control systems, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SY (Control Systems) are also possible categories. Finally, the paper discusses the challenges and future of SLAM, which is related to artificial intelligence, so cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category.
